API_Description: The type of annotation. The type of an annotation can only be set within the object-literal argument of the Doc object addAnnot method. The valid values are: * Text * FreeText * Line * Square * Circle * Polygon * PolyLine * Highlight * Underline * Squiggly * StrikeOut * Stamp * Caret * Ink * FileAttachment * Sound **Annotations** : All
